{
  "stem": "11144.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was very far to him, and very strange and alien.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my mother was really take-- undertaking the responsibility of them leaving.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were writing-- and I can blame myself for that-- that I was writing very bad letters, that it's very hard and the situation is tough.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and I think, because of that, they remained.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They turned back in the papers and whatever, and they remained.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to Ulpan and-- for half a year and I learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after that, I got a job as an economist in an Israeli firm, and I was working.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to leave Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very happy there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, in the beginning, I was miserable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was, you know, missing my-- I was very close with my mother, very close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I still remember the pain I had when I was saying goodbye to her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a physical, physical pain, like somebody took a knife and cut my heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's how painful that was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I was really missing her and I was missing my sister, my stepfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, I guess, the whole culture.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very strange.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But after half a year or a year, I really got acclimated there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had a job and we had a-- we got a very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had a lot of family in Israel from my father's side, and all our friends came, little by little, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we really had a nice-- very nice social life, everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But my husband's family was here in America-- his father and his sister and his brother-in-law-- and he decided that there was not enough room for him to grow in Israel, and he begged me to go.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
